Employee Management System
This is a console-based employee management system implemented in Kotlin that allows you to add, list, search, remove, and update employee information as well as generate payslips for employees.

Features
Add a new employee by entering their first name, surname, gender, gross salary, PAYE percentage, PRSI percentage, annual bonus, and cycle to work monthly deduction.
List all employees and display their information.
Search for an employee by entering their employee ID.
Remove an employee by entering their employee ID.
Update an employee's details by entering their employee ID and updating their first name, surname, gender, gross salary, PAYE percentage, PRSI percentage, annual bonus, and cycle to work monthly deduction.
Generate a payslip for an employee by entering their employee ID.
Logging
